snippet.title: Toy Tactics - Official Trailer | Future Games Show 2024
snippet.description:
Here's a look at Toy Tactics, a physics-based RTS game. Control armies inspired by minifigs in Mercenary, Puzzle, and Sandbox modes. Draw unit formations and power up your army with powerful spells and artifacts.

Toy Tactics is coming to PC (Steam) on September 19, 2024.

#ToyTactics #Gaming #Games
